name: isovaleryl-CoA dehydrogenase
classes: Acting on the CH-CH group of donors;
reaction: isovaleryl-CoA + electron-transfer flavoprotein = 3-methylcrotonyl-CoA + reduced electron-transfer flavoprotein [RN:R04096]
comment: Contains FAD as prosthetic group. Pentanoate can act as donor.
